## Appendix D: Leibnitz Equality by Hand

0\. $\equiv (\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota)))~(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b) (P_{o\iota} a)))$

1\. $\neg(\equiv (\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota)))~(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b) (P_{o\iota} a))))$ $\quad$ Tableaux initialization

_Branch A:_

2\. $\neg (\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota)))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

3\. $\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b_\iota) (P_{o\iota} a_\iota))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

4\. $\supset (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\neg\Pi (2)$

_Branch AA:_

5\. $\neg (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\supset (4)$

6\. $\supset (\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota) (\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} a)$ $\quad$ $\Pi (3)$

_Branch AAA:_

7\. $\neg (\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\supset (6)$

$\star$ with $\sigma^1 = \{\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} \gets (\lambda X_\iota. \neg (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota))\}$

_Branch AAB (including $\sigma^1$):_

8\. $\neg (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\supset (6)$

Reinstantiation necessary

_Branch AB:_

?\. $\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota$ $\quad$ $\supset (4)$

_Branch B:_

?\. $\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

??\. $\neg(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b) (P_{o\iota} a)))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

```elixir
# unification to close branch AAA:
a = mk_const_term("a", type_i)
b = mk_const_term("b", type_i)
sk1 = mk_const_term("sk1", type_io)
x1 = mk_free_var_term("X1", type_io)

neg_line_5 = mk_appl_term(neg_term, mk_appl_term(neg_term, mk_appl_term(sk1, a)))
line_7 = mk_appl_term(neg_term, mk_appl_term(x1, b))

PrettyPrint.pp_term(neg_line_5) |> IO.puts()
PrettyPrint.pp_term(line_7) |> IO.puts()

unify({line_7, neg_line_5}) |> PrettyPrint.pp_res()
```
